These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-1::.
House: cape-cod, townhouse, farmhouse, craftsman, gothic-revival, futuristic
6 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, chess, snooker, whist, go
1. the person playing scrabble is the cape-cod house##1
2. the craftsman house is the person playing go##1
3. the farmhouse house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the person playing scrabble is between the person playing go and the person playing whist##2
5. the person playing whist is in an even position##4
6. the person playing billiard is on the far right##1
7. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
8. the futuristic house is the person playing chess##1
9. the cape-cod house is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |     3      |  4   |     5      |    6    |
| House         | gothic-revival     | farmhouse | cape-cod | craftsman | futuristic      | townhouse |
| Game   | snooker | whist  | scrabble    | go | chess | billiard    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: daisy, poppy, rose, sunflower, zinnia, marigold
City: boston, san-francisco, colone, rome, berlin, edinburgh
 1. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 2. the person traveling to rome is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
 5. the person who growsrose is the person traveling to rome##1
 6. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 7. the person traveling to colone is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person traveling to berlin is in an even position##4
 9. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
10. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |      5      |    6    |
| Flower   | daisy  | sunflower  | zinnia | poppy   | marigold | rose |
| City   | colone | berlin | san-francisco    | edinburgh | boston   | rome   |

