.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-4::.
6 different pets are kept: pony, cat, fish, mouse, goat, guinea-pig
The people have 6 different jobs:  nurse, firefighter, freelancer, architect, manager, pilot
1. the nurse is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the architect##3
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
4. the architect is in an even position##4
5. the freelancer is the owner of the fish##1
6. the firefighter is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
7. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
8. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
9. the pilot is on the left of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Pet   | pony | cat     | fish     | mouse | goat | guinea-pig |
| Job     | pilot    | firefighter | freelancer | architect  | manager       | nurse      |

