.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-5::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: january, august, may, march, february, december
There are 6 different nationalities: egyptian, dutch, pakistani, chinese, argentine, indonesian
 1. the chinese is between the person who's birthday is in may and the pakistani##2
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is the indonesian##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the argentine##1
 4. the argentine is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the indonesian is on the right of the argentine##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the chinese##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
10. the pakistani is on the left or right of the egyptian##3
11. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
12. the chinese is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |     4      |     5      |    6    |
| Birthday   | february | march | january | december    | may    | august |
| Nationality     | dutch         | egyptian       | pakistani  | chinese | argentine | indonesian   |

