City: marseilles, edinburgh, paris, prague, boston, miami
 1. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who likes brown##1
 2. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 3. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 4. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 5. the person who likes apricot is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who likes purple is in an odd position##4
 7. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
 8. the person who likes fuchsia is the person traveling to prague##1
 9. the person who likes apricot is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6    |
| Color   | apricot   | yellow   | fuchsia    | chestnut    | purple  | brown   |
| City   | miami | paris | prague | marseilles | boston | edinburgh |

