.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: romance, western, fantasy, epic, zombie, musical
There 6 different types of food: nectarine, pomegranate, pear, zucchini, broccoli, grapes
 1. the person eating grapes is the person watching musical movies##1
 2. the person eating broccoli is on the left or right of the person watching epic movies##3
 3. the person eating nectarine is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
 4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 6. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 7. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
 8. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
 9. the person watching romance movies is in an even position##4
10. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2       |         3          |    4     |     5     |   6    |
| Movie-Genre     | epic | western     | zombie | romance  | fantasy     | musical |
| Food   | pomegranate         | broccoli | zucchini              | pear | nectarine | grapes |

