.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-4-10::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: superhero, epic, adventure, satire, spy, western
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: dubstep, soul, folk, house, jazz, funk
 1. the fan of house is between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching spy movies##2
 2. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
 3. the fan of funk is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 4. the person watching western movies is the fan of house##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
 6. the fan of folk is on the far right##1
 7. the fan of folk is the person watching epic movies##1
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the fan of folk##3
 9. the person watching superhero movies is the fan of jazz##1
10. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
11. the person watching superhero movies is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |       3       |   4   |     5     |    6    |
| Movie-Genre    | superhero | satire | adventure | western | spy      | epic    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz       | funk      | soul     | house  | dubstep | folk |

