 1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
 2. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
 3. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 4. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
 5. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 6. the person drinking cola is the person who growsbellflower##1
 7. the person drinking tea is in an even position##4
 8. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
 9. the person who growsdahlia is between the person drinking juice and the person who growspoppy##2
10. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
11. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
12. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |      2      |   3    |   4    |       5        |     6      |
| Beverage   | cola    | tea      | fanta  | juice  | soy-milk           | 7up  |
